  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p>Feel the rush of the mountain air on an Inghams Ski weekend or flexible trip. </p>
<p>At Inghams we take care of the detail, you can choose from a wide variety of departure airports and flight schedules, hassle free transfers and in resort support.</p>
<p>Our short breaks to <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-late-deals/ski-short-breaks/france-ski-short-breaks">France</a> are perfect for the time conscious skier, <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-late-deals/ski-short-breaks/switzerland-ski-short-breaks">Switzerland</a> uses the efficient Swiss rail services to transfer you to resort, a weekend escape to <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-late-deals/ski-short-breaks/Italy-ski-short-breaks">Italy</a> blends days on the slopes with fine Italian cuisine and wine. <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-late-deals/ski-short-breaks/austria-ski-short-breaks">Austria</a> offers short transfers and legendary Apres Ski. </p>
<p>With early, outbound departures and direct transfers you will be on the slopes before you know it, spending an entire weekend skiing. Escaping the hustle and bustle of everyday life is the perfect end to a busy week.</p>
<p><span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; color: #023761;">What’s included in our Ski Short Breaks?</span></p>
<ul>
<li>Daily departures from many U.K airports</li>
<li>Flexible durations from 2 nights</li>
<li>Transfer via taxi, train or minibus</li>
<li>Rep service in all resorts</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div> </div>
<p><span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; color: #023761;">Our short break destinations</span></p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #023761;">France</span></p>
<p><img src="/media/13056602/rockypop-hotel-fac-ade-e-te-hd-1.jpg" alt="Hotel Rockypop in Chamonix" rel="838,360" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 21px; font-weight: bold; color: #023761;">Hotel Rockypop</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/25976b79e286484388471003fee6da97" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25976b79e286484388471003fee6da97}" title="Rockypop Hotel">Hotel Rockypop</a> is situated on the border of Chamonix and Les Houches, the hotel provides a Rocky Shuttle bus to Brévent, Flégère, Grands Montets and Le Tour four times daily.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #023761;">Switzerland</span></p>
<p><img src="/media/13063847/switzerland_graubuenden-ski-region_davos_skier-piste-action.jpg" alt="Skiing in Davos" rel="840,401" /></p>
<p>Inghams Ski weekends and short breaks make the most of the efficient Swiss rail services from Geneva or Zurich to get you to your chosen resort, superb half board hotels and ski areas make it a great short break destination. Choose from the world class resorts of <a data-udi="umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/b23ef1df250240c5a3657f721fdb96d0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b23ef1df250240c5a3657f721fdb96d0}" title="Klosters">Klosters</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95de5322c984f85bcf0f013c457e8df}" title="Davos">Davos</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/1597219bc8c942e685b083f42d203f8f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1597219bc8c942e685b083f42d203f8f}" title="Arosa-Lenzerheide">Arosa</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55}" title="St. Moritz">St Moritz</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #023761;">Italy</span></p>
<p><img src="/media/13068213/presstripcolumbia_aiacebazzana-_low-403.jpg" alt="" rel="840,401" /></p>
<p>Ski and board in the shadow of Mont Blanc in the resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/6001103ad3884b75a70ed71efd274ef8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6001103ad3884b75a70ed71efd274ef8}" title="Courmayeur">Courmayeur</a>, this small town offers superb Italian hospitality and cuisine. You also have the opportunity to access the superb off piste and ski touring on the slopes of Mont Blanc and its sister peaks using the Sky Way Monte Biano lift or Courmayeur is one of the rare locations in the alps from which you can Heliski or ski the Valley Blanche starting from the Italian side ending in <a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a> before taking a taxi of bus back to Courmayeur.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #023761;">Austria</span></p>
<p><img src="/media/13051929/austria_kuhtai_resort-view-southern-slopes.jpg" alt="View of southern slopes in Kühtai in Austria" rel="840,401" /></p>
<p>Some of the shortest transfers from airport to resort, world famous apres ski. Austria is a great location for a short ski break and one that is sometime overlooked. Choose from <a data-udi="umb://document/01a44a65274b461ea52482a089f2f76c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/01a44a65274b461ea52482a089f2f76c}" title="Kuhtai">Kuhtai</a> with its easily accessible off piste and great piste skiing or <a data-udi="umb://document/9d356beed1384469aaaa32e2ceb11b4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9d356beed1384469aaaa32e2ceb11b4a}" title="Igls">Igls</a> which is the closest resort to Innsbruck which allows you combine skiing and relaxing in Innsbruck.</p>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
